	<DisplayName Value="Moving Away Fix" />
	<!--Short description of the mod-->
	<ShortDescription Value="Stops moving-away cims from walking along highways by letting them use transport again." />
	<!--Long description of the mod. Single line or multi line. Supports minimal markdown subset-->
	<!--LongDescription Value="This is a long description" /-->
	<LongDescription>
Fixes moving-away cims that end up with IgnoreTransport and walk long distances toward an outside connection.

When enabled, the mod clears that flag for moving-away residents and marks their path obsolete so vanilla can repath them onto public transport.

No Harmony patches.
	</LongDescription>
